.Dd March 2, 1999
.Dt NETGROUP 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm netgroup
.Nd list netgroup members
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl dhu
.Ar netgroup
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
lists the members of specified netgroups.  The type of members
is selected using the following options:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl d
list domains
.It Fl h
list hosts (the default)
.It Fl u
list users
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr innetgr 1 ,
.Xr netgroup 5
.Sh HISTORY
A
.Nm
utility appeared in
.Nx 1.4 .
